name: Speed Work: 600m Intervals
description:
Frost this morning but still shorts and tshirt weather!
Was tired of being fast on the track and slow on the road so I actually measured 600m according to Strava. 
Goal: 10x600m in 2:12 (3:40 pace)
Actual: 2:06, 2:05, 2:05, 2:06, 2:08, 2:09, 2:09, 2:07, 2:05 (I guess music really helps!) 2:04
